Package booking.model

Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
booking.model.Reservation
public class Reservation extends Object
The Reservation class represents a booking made by a user. It contains details about the reservation's start date, end date, associated user, hotel, and room.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Andres Feldstedt
